   wrapper added Laplace noise to every numeric field ŌĆö including `ts`,
   `http_code`, `latency_ms`, `tokens_in`, `tokens_out` ŌĆö corrupting Merkle
   ordering, breaking the audit oracle, and silently violating the immutable
   audit-trail doctrine. The `try/except ImportError` fallback to clean writes
   never triggered because the orphan module file exists on disk.
   FIX: Removed the import; restored deterministic clean append. Verified ts
   and http_code are now exact (no noise) via patched `time.time` test.

2. `System/swarm_boot.py` heartbeat loop was calling
   `swarm_entropy_throttle.entropy_factor()` to scale `BASE_SLEEP_S`. The
   function was returning 2.0 in idle (no visual data) ŌĆö halving every cadence
   in the entire organism. This is the inverted logic + sensor-range mismatch
   C47H called out.
   FIX: Reverted to `current_base_sleep = BASE_SLEEP_S`.

3. `System/swarm_boot.py` was also calling
   `swarm_quantum_scheduler.select_subsystem()` and using the result to gate
